# To run this project you must follow the steps above:

```
$ git clone https://github.com/42Paris/minilibx-linux
$ cd minilibx-linux
$ sh ./configure

$ sudo apt-get install libxext-dev libxrandr-dev libx11-dev libbsd-dev libssl-dev
&& make
&& sudo mv libmlx.a /usr/local/lib/
&& sudo mv mlx.h /usr/local/include/
```

# To check if everything is ok run minilibx tests
```
$ cd test/
$ ./run_tests.sh
```